{"tid":870974,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"想搵返套細個睇過嘅驚慄片","createTime":"2018-10-21T14:14:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-21T14:45:28.000Z","uid":2797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ad2dd8c2ab8a7844073c345d8d8c55e1055582ce","tid":870974,"uid":2797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T14:14:15.000Z","msg":"套戲大概就係講有個殺人犯，我唔記得係咪以保母身份入嚟照顧啲小朋友，因為父母要出門<br />\n<br />\n總之係喺一間大屋入面，大屋中間有個類似日式水池/庭園咁嘅物體，有好多植物<br />\n成套戲就係講個殺人犯鎖晒間屋要捉啲人嚟殺，追追逐逐咁<br />\n<br />\n然後有一幕係個細佬匿左喺水池嘅橋下面，個殺人犯係上面經過搵佢唔到，個細佬喺下面透過啲罅望上去<br />\n<br />\n概念圖（戲入面係木橋嚟）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/21/220602_3876a8407bb381ee18e33baf1a108065.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F21%2F220602_3876a8407bb381ee18e33baf1a108065.png&h=2a614d04&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有一幕係講其中一個人逃走到去門口，匿左喺門口隔離個櫃入面，但都係俾人發現左<br />\n<br />\n套戲最後係喺夜晚，然後有好多警車嚟到捉左條友，仲喺警車入面啤返主角之類<br />\n<br />\n細個同老母睇完驚左好多年，我諗都有成十年前，記憶模糊，而家想睇返但唔知叫咩名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n跪求戲名<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd9030c5ccd3c31414b3e45a0d158a2de8c4e1ca","tid":870974,"uid":212625,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T14:28:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=z-dbpSmMUaI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dz-dbpSmMUaI&d=sxJE5pEKs1Lj8wXYeMwTMQHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=538b1f33\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=z-dbpSmMUaI</a><br />\nThis?"},{"pid":"c7a8179b1b0e6634700427d1d1b0d6951218cd9d","tid":870974,"uid":2797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bd9030c5ccd3c31414b3e45a0d158a2de8c4e1ca","tid":870974,"uid":212625,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T14:28:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=z-dbpSmMUaI\" data-sr-url=\"https://